quran[7]{c,v,t}:
  39,68,"Wuttee ka Allaandu, kala ko woni ka kammuuli e ka leydi kon faɗɗee, si wanaa ɓen ɓe Allah muuyani [daɗugol]. Refti wuttee e mayru ɗiɗaɓol, tawa ko ɓe dariiɓe habbitii"
  39,69,"Leydi ndin jalbira ndaygo Jeydo ndi On; taalkuru ndun wallinee, Annabaaɓe e seedeeɓe maɓɓe ɓen addee; goonga ñaawiree hakkunde maɓɓe, wanaa ɓe tooñeteeɓe"
  39,70,"wonki kala yoɓee ko golli kon. Ko Kanko [Allah] ɓuri anndude ko ɓe gollata"
  39,71,"Yedduɓe ɓen soggiroyee ka Jahannama dente-dente. Haa si ɓe hewtii nge, dame magge udditee, reenuɓe nge ɓen wi'ana ɓe: \"E Nulaaɓe jeyaaɓe e mo'on hewtaano on, janngaynooɓe Aayeeje Joomi mon, e mooɗon, ɓe rentina on hawrugol e ndee ñalaande mon?\" Ɓe wi'a: \"Ko non tigiri, kono Konngol lepte ngol, jojjiino e yedduɓe ɓen"
  39,72,"[Ɓe] wi'anee: \"Naatiree dame Jahannama ɗen lutton ton. Nge bonii jaaƴorde mawnintiniiɓe ɓen"
  39,73,"Hulooɓe Joomi mun ɓen kadi ɗowitiree ka Aljanna, dente-dente. Haa si ɓe hewtii mo, dame makko udditee, reenuɓe mo ɓen wi'ana ɓe: \"Kisiyee wonii e mon, on laaɓii, naatiree mo, duumagol"
  39,74,"Ɓe wi'a ontuma: \"Yettoore woodanii Allah, laatinanɗo men fodoore Mun, O ronini men leydi [Aljanna] ndin, meɗen weerira e Aljanna on, kala ka men yiɗi\". Mbarjaari gollunooɓe moƴƴere ɓen moƴƴii"